  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>RELAX, REJUVENATE AND REVIVE IN 2016 WITH INGHAMS’ HEALTH KICK SKI RETREATS</p>
<p><strong>Wednesday 20th January 2016, London</strong> – The start of a new year brings the beginning of a new health and fitness resolution for most, with an ever enthusiastic attitude for starting a new regime. To help its guests kick off their New Year with a health-driven approach, ski holiday specialists Inghams is offering a revival break to the stylish town of <a data-udi="umb://document/2dcb1a3292da421780aa165d449493a9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2dcb1a3292da421780aa165d449493a9}" title="Cortina D’Ampezzo">Cortina D’Ampezzo</a> in<a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy"> Italy</a>, along with a ski and Pilates retreat in the <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austrian</a> resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/415e45d2352b4e61b39f1f3f2a9ec53d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/415e45d2352b4e61b39f1f3f2a9ec53d}" title="St Christoph">St. Christoph.</a></p>
<p>The perfect new you revival in Cortina D’Ampezzo, Italy <br />The best kick start workout is beckoning in the chic ski town of Cortina d’Ampezzo, the Queen of the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites</a> in northern Italy, presenting the perfect solution for reviving and refreshing after an indulgent 2015. Following its success last season, Cortina has been transformed into the first Technogym Mountain Wellness Hub. Guests can take their fitness regime onto the mountain to enjoy four days of sport and wellness with Cortina’s alpine guides. Day one features a freeride tour between Tofana and Lagazuoi, finishing in the Lagazuoi refuge where, at 2,752m, guests can relax in the highest altitude sauna in the Dolomites. Day two is a freeride excursion in the Lagazuoi Val Travenanzes five Torri area finishing at the Scoiattoli refuge at 2,255m to unwind in the outdoor hot tub. Day three is a ski mountaineering route across Forcella Averau to Passo Giau and on to the Croda da Lago Refuge to try its Finnish sauna and finally, day four includes a climb over the majestic Rocchetta di Prendera, before heading back down to Cortina.</p>
<p>Inghams is offering seven nights, chalet board at the four diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/d1b25faa2e9640028bb897b344b3d2d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d1b25faa2e9640028bb897b344b3d2d8}" title="Chalet Hotel Parc Victoria">Chalet Hotel Parc Victoria</a>, Cortina, Italy from £599 per person with a saving of £180 per person. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Innsbruck and resort transfers, departing on 6th February 2016. For more information, or to book, visit www.inghams.co.uk or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><strong>Ski, Snow and Pilates in Austria</strong> <br />Pilates has become as popular as ever and is a great way of improving core strength, developing flexibility, control and endurance – all key skills for skiers in order to be agile and fit for the slopes. During a Pilates class, skiers can develop their muscles correctly, helping them to prevent injury, as well as to relax and recuperate after a thrilling day of skiing or snowboarding. Inghams has introduced a new Pilates class for guests staying in the 4.5 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/c08f16ba779a4d33987f63acecd04ac0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c08f16ba779a4d33987f63acecd04ac0}" title="Chalet Hotel St. Christoph">Chalet Hotel St. Christoph</a>, Austria to experience whilst enjoying a week of fantastic skiing in St. Christoph, which has 340 km of slopes.</p>
<p>Inghams is offering seven nights, half board (including skiers’ buffet breakfast, afternoon tea and a five course evening meal with complimentary wine) at the 4.5 diamond, ski-in/ski-out Chalet Hotel St. Christoph, Austria from £769 per person departing on 27th February or 5th March 2016. Price includes return flights from London Gatwick to Friedrichshafen airport and resort transfers. Guests departing on these dates will receive a complimentary one hour Pilates class each evening, Monday to Friday. For more information, or to book, visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114.</p>
<p><br />For more information and ski holiday packages visit <br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays">www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays</a><br />or call 01483 79 11 14</p>
